#========================
# README for simulation
# 2019.05.23 updated 


* File Composition
  - sim.{ip_name}.fnc
    : run simulation
    : user defined
  - top_tb.v
    : include tb_{ip_name}.v
    : include dump.{ip_name}.v
    : +@ 
  - dump.{ip_name}.v
    : defined dump scope
  - tb_{ip_name}.v
    : ip specific testbench
  - filelist.{ip_name}.f
    : ip specific filelist
  - rtl/*.v
    : source files
  - 


* Generated Files
  - dump/dump.{ip_name}.fnc.fsdb
    : generated dump file
  - log/sim.{ip_name}.fnc.log
    : generated log file
  - 


* Simulation Lists
  - duv
    : simple mux.
  - arbiter
    : simple arbiter
    : 2-req signals, 2-gnt signals
  - 


